<plot>Anna has turned old. She lives in her apartment with the memories of her husband. Waiting only for the end. Annas son Henrik wants to end her misery. But Anna doesn't want help - she just wants to be seen. Her grandchild Lise understands, though standing between the two stubborn heads of the family. Water falls from the ceiling and lands on the floor...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?017212</url></doc>
